Problem Statement:
Given a singly linked list with N nodes and a number X. The task is to find the node at the given index (X)(1 based index) of linked list. 

Solution:
public static int getNth(Node node, int ind)
    {
       Node temp=node;
       int counter=1;
       while(counter<ind)
       {
           temp=temp.next;
           ++counter;
       }
       return temp.data;
    }
